      <p>In order to demonstrate the potential of IDOPS to investigate the genetic context of pesticidal proteins, we tested our tool against known reported <italic>cry1</italic> cassettes in plasmids of <italic>B. thuringiensis</italic> (<xref ref-type="fig" rid="F2">Figure 2</xref>).</p>
